{"tid":2265024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沉𨳒民呢條仆街冚家產賤種都有人讚好官，痴撚線","createTime":"2020-10-31T06:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T07:58:28.000Z","uid":276415,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe74cfe085f2463db6b5dc75fa5b1e80d2591352","tid":2265024,"uid":276415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:09:41.000Z","msg":"2017 - 至於第三被告薛達榮自辯時稱，自己當晚與朋友唱卡拉OK之後到場看熱鬧，為安全起見，「人跑他又跑」，但法官反駁這說法站不住腳，他稱如果不想被誤以為示威者，應該站在原位不動，而非跟示威者做相同的事，跟著人跑反而可能人踩人，法官裁定三人暴動罪罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次 - 沒有證據顯示被告做了什麼，強調被告僅是身在現場，不足以證明有罪。即使被告逃跑，亦可以有其他清白原因，例如應警方警告離開，或因當時社會環境而對警方產生恐懼，並非一定源於畏罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角騷亂三人暴動罪成　法官：當晚實屬暴動<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=214351&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D214351%26refer%3DShare&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=275637df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D214351%26refer%3DShare&h=e9e1abb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=214351&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"f319bd3143e4d9a1a375aabbb3258ff4b8bdbe1a","tid":2265024,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"因為中共要吹香港有司法獨立叫黨友放生警暴受害人保經濟利益<br />\n<br />\n而大律師公會要保法院形象穩住國際仲裁水所以幫手派牌"},{"pid":"213ffcbc001f3ebc05e9b4abf5b0f942c0820052","tid":2265024,"uid":276415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f319bd3143e4d9a1a375aabbb3258ff4b8bdbe1a","tid":2265024,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sco